Property and Casualty Application

Renew policies with a couple of clicks, make use of the new harmonized business process, and more in the Property and Casualty Application.

Commissions for Vlocity Insurance Application Suite
You can now track commissions for agents and insurance products, and gain insight into commissions associated with each stage of the customer journey.
Harmonized Auto FNOL Claims Process
This business process writes to the harmonized Claims process which now supports both the existing Vlocity and FSC object model (custom objects in managed package) and the new Salesforce object model (standard Salesforce objects).
Renew Policies
Now, a couple of clicks is all it takes to renew a policy for all lines of business.
